      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata - Uff. Rev. Stampa Milano 11-6-17 N 1139 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>[Donna sdraiata]</head>
               <figDesc> Donna (in azzurro) sdraiata sul letto con un cuscino giallo
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Modena lì 3/9 - 1917</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Oliva mia cara, <lb/>            domenica e lunedì senza un tuo scritto, <lb/>            senza un tuo dolcisfimo bacio che è tan - <lb/>            ta forte del mio cuore. Perchè così?<lb/>            Io so tu vorrai ch'io corra da te a por -  <lb/>            tarti le delizie dell'animo mio, tutto <lb/>            il mio affetto carezzevole i miei sentimen - <lb/>            ti pieni di ardore, il mio amore fuori ci <lb/>            sono la luce, l'aria, la vita l'azzurro <lb/>            gli ideali più santi e più nobili. <lb/>            Lo so è il mio stufo anelito!<lb/>            Un desiderio che mi agita tutto, un <lb/>            mondo di misteri, un arcano infinito <lb/>            di luce strana, suggestionatrice, tanta <lb/>            parte di me stufo, la più bella, la più <lb/>            potente, inoperosa, inattiva e il <lb/>            rammarico atroce dei giorni che pasfano <lb/>            la vita che s'invola dal dominio della <lb/>            giovinezza bella, fascinatrice. <lb/>            Oliva ma, ma, non volgio più così, <lb/>            amami, amami sempre meglio.<lb/>            Mille leggerisfime carezze tuo, tuo, tuo </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 113 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
